===Pronunciation===
*Rhymes: [[Rhymes:English:-əʊlt|-əʊlt]]

===Verb===
'''revolt'''

# to [[rebel]], particularly against authority
#:''The farmers had to '''revolt''' against the government to get what they deserve''
# to greatly [[repel]]
#:''Your brother ''revolts''' me!''

